{"tid":2256180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東九龍總區重案組明早會晤潘曉穎母親「了解」其需要","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T07:38:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"88eadcb75d3744205e40e6f0d6975bb8f6f5655e","tid":2256180,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"警方明早晤潘曉穎母親<br />\n<br />\n台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳昨日出獄滿一年，至今仍未到台灣投案。消息指，警方昨晚致電案中受害人潘曉穎母親，並約定明天早上會面，希望了解潘太的需要，警方東九龍總區重案組會負責與潘太的聯絡工作。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，昨日致電案中死者潘曉穎的母親，了解事件最新情況，並會與她保持聯絡及提供適切可行的協助。潘曉穎的母親透過中間人向傳媒表示指，晚上9時接獲警方電話，但警方只是聯絡她交還涉及洗黑錢案中女兒的證物，並非關於她近日提出希望當中間人，邀請香港及台灣警方坐下商討，她仍希望香港警方就此盡快跟她聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2363131&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=4d83d211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363131</a>"},{"pid":"50429f47c5ef38b43128ebd138dff7cc708395f9","tid":2256180,"uid":126731,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"準備拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d725b164ad7f003207d2ba4dc726a54bf2f007","tid":2256180,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"性需要"},{"pid":"171b1f151d7b957390a704dae3e05c2ade66a61a","tid":2256180,"uid":83582,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"恐嚇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3adc5cbdbac66c130ba65175298449c2eb9f032","tid":2256180,"uid":9328,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"之前用lan線，上次用長褲，今次用咩呢？"},{"pid":"551bf664f5214b48eee918e47641aecfb1945658","tid":2256180,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3adc5cbdbac66c130ba65175298449c2eb9f032","tid":2256180,"uid":9328,"like":4,"dislik